1
00:00:00,760 --> 00:00:01,760
Relax, Light.

2
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:03,977
While it's true that Kira
hates losing, it's also

3
00:00:03,978 --> 00:00:06,240
true that most people
would rather win than lose.

4
00:00:06,380 --> 00:00:07,380
It's human nature.

5
00:00:08,560 --> 00:00:10,940
Is he going to think that I'm Kira if I go
for the win?

6
00:00:11,140 --> 00:00:12,980
I suppose I could just lose on purpose.

7
00:00:13,220 --> 00:00:15,060
But if I do, it could work against me.

8
00:00:15,220 --> 00:00:17,726
Since he'd expect Kira to
want to win, he might also

9
00:00:17,727 --> 00:00:20,121
expect me to throw the
match to avoid suspicion.

10
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:24,260
I don't see any way that he can profile me
based on a tennis match.

11
00:00:24,640 --> 00:00:27,940
So, I have to assume he has some other
goal in mind.

12
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:33,740
Either way, I'm not going to let him win.

13
00:00:38,360 --> 00:00:39,460
Look at that.

14
00:00:39,920 --> 00:00:41,260
He's going for the win.

15
00:00:41,800 --> 00:00:43,120
That's four games all.

16
00:00:43,440 --> 00:00:44,740
Light Yagami to serve.

